text: Changaiz Ahmed Khan Kakar is a Pakistan Politician who is a Member of the National Assembly from February 29, 2024 to date. He has also been a Member of Punjab Bar Council (laywers highest pronvincial regulatory body) for 3 consecutive terms from 2010 to 2015 (each term comprising of 5 years). He succeeded Chuadhary Abid Sher Ali in 2024 general elections. ==References== Category:Politicians from Punjab, Pakistan
title: Changaiz Ahmed Khan Kakar
